nodes.bodyText:
@brastak we have some restrictions for repository names, see https://github.com/artipie/artipie

Make sure that the name of your config file is the name of repository you are going to host, and its name matches [a-z0-9_]{3,32}

So, I've changed it to [a-zA-Z0-9_]

